Nigeria’s President Muhammadu Buhari has received the governor of Bayelsa state, Duoye Diri at the Presidential villa, Abuja. Details of their discussion is yet to be made public. The photos were shared on social media by Buhari’s aide, Bashir Ahmad, who wrote: “President @MBuhari receives in audience Bayelsa State Governor H.E. Duoye Diri this afternoon at the State House, Abuja-BA.” Source